title: Softball Drops Contest to Tennessee Tech, 5-3 - University of Tennessee at Chattanooga Athletics - GoMocs.com
content: Softball Drops Contest to Tennessee Tech, 5-3 - University of Tennessee at Chattanooga Athletics  GoMocs.com
description: CHATTANOOGA – The Chattanooga Mocs' softball team was unable to overcome a 5-0 third-inning deficit against the visiting Tennessee Tech Golden Eagles on Tuesday afternoon at Frost Stadium. The Golden Eagles took the game 5-3.
